data.description: Amazing deal! It's a new home without the long wait!  Lovely 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home in desirable zip code 34953 Near Tradition. This home features granite counters in the bathrooms and kitchen.  The living are has a beautiful open floorplan that opens to the gorgeous kitchen stocked with stainless steel appliances.  Perfect for hosting and enjoying loved ones.  The home is energy efficient and has smart home features like a ring doorbell.  The backyard has plenty of room for a pool.  Close to tradition without the HOA fees.  Seller is paying buyer's closing costs! Easy highway access and shopping nearby.
